<p>Unleash your inner detective and solve the case! Enjoy an unforgettable day of intrigue and suspense while exploring the immersive setting at Cumberland Heritage Village Museum. Work together with family and friends to piece together all the clues before time runs out. A buffet-style brunch, featuring a menu of classic and delicious breakfast foods, will be served.</p>
